    "feature_1_label": "01",
    "feature_1_title": "AI Agents",
    "feature_1_subtitle": "From dashboards to decisions and action",
    "feature_1_body": "Most organisations already have rich dashboards and KPIs. We build <strong>AI agents on top of them</strong>: systems that query your data through tools, run <strong>what-if simulations</strong>, and go beyond answers – they <strong>act</strong> and produce the artefacts a decision actually needs, from briefings and reports to updated records – all with a traceable log of every step.",
    "feature_2_label": "02",
    "feature_2_title": "Experiment & Lab Platforms",
    "feature_2_subtitle": "Enabling research experiments end-to-end",
    "feature_2_body": "We build <strong>systems for experiments and labs</strong>: multi-module <strong>online experiments</strong>, social robots that interview visitors, <strong>AI coding of open-ended responses</strong> with built-in reliability metrics, and tools that <strong>instrument real web behavior</strong> as structured data.",
    "feature_2_body_2": "Alongside the visible systems, we deliver the <strong>enabling infrastructure</strong> – data pipelines, tool APIs, experiment modules, and sensor sync – tailored to your lab. It's the work behind our own products, <strong>qualcode.ai</strong> and <strong>labrowser.app</strong>.",
