    "feature_3_body": "We bring <strong>research-level rigor</strong> to every project: reproducible builds, versioned infrastructure, tested components, clear audit trails, and focused performance work where it matters – so research institutes and companies can run ambitious systems and experiments without fragile prototypes.",
